class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Application\\Handler\\MessageIdempotencyService"
type: final class
summary: Ensures message idempotency by tracking processed execution keys within specific scopes and run contexts. It prevents duplicate processing of identical idempotency keys for the same logical operation.
